<h4 id="what-next">What next?</h4>

<p>Bank holiday Monday and then a show and tell. The team have been doing some excellent sharing, but want to make sure we are showing whatever we have done every fortnight, preferably as design work (prototypes etc) and research work (sessions and analysis). Outcomes over jazzy presentations. Framing everything with some context is something we are OK at but need to get better at, more concise and as a matter of habit.</p>

<p>I need to get some of the â€œtoolsâ€ represented clearer on the service map.</p>

